{"type": "article", "id": 12558, "title": "Daniel Wellington 加入日期功能", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:09:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000206lJFxGLytcugm9z6V.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tDapper Collection by Daniel Wellington\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t手表品牌 Daniel Wellington 以其清新简单的设计，百搭的特点迅速风靡全球，几乎成为最快蹿红的手表品牌。近来，他们推出了新系列 Dapper Collection，在沿袭经典款简约设计的同时，为手表加入了日期功能，这个系列将于今年 10 月 1 日开始发售，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/manager/articles/12553/www.danielwellington.com\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140312yieFdr3UGn5goQwW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140312AbcV8oDunHY9KdpJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140312PYCog3OQd7DBsGSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261403130v5kmiN7l4gf8aIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}